The last two weekends, we've been focusing one verse each weekend, something to hold on to through the winds and the waves that life may bring.

00:26.146 --> 00:31.713
The first weekend, if you remember, we focused on Pastor Up Taught, Romans 828, 828.

00:32.495 --> 00:37.261
