01:22.445 --> 01:29.538
Some verses are like an anchor that will keep you where you need to be, where you can stand firm through the storm.

01:30.239 --> 01:35.249
And some verses, if you think about what an anchor looks like, I don't know why I was thinking about it.

01:35.269 --> 01:38.195
