01:38.215 --> 01:42.002
And it's not just anchor verses that keep us where we are.

01:42.242 --> 01:49.530
but a grappling hook that we can shoot and it will anchor somewhere far off into the distance and it will get us where we need to go.

01:49.571 --> 01:56.599
This week's anchor verse, Psalm 37.4 is a grappling hook verse.

01:57.380 --> 01:58.261
