Delight yourself in the Lord and He shall give you the desires of your heart.

02:33.951 --> 02:35.794
Delight yourself in the Lord.

02:36.034 --> 02:38.818
And He shall give you the desires of your heart.

02:38.838 --> 02:39.499
Let's say it together.

02:39.820 --> 02:41.783
Delight yourself in the Lord.

02:41.843 --> 02:45.508
And He shall give you the desires of your heart.

02:45.989 --> 02:47.191
