02:51.177 --> 02:56.485
He shall bring forth your righteousness as the light and your justice as the noon day.

02:57.026 --> 02:57.967
Rest in the Lord.

02:58.068 --> 02:59.730
Wait patiently for Him.

03:00.194 --> 03:09.068
Do not fret because of him who prospers in his way, because of the man who brings wicked schemes to pass, cease from anger and forsake wrath.

03:09.228 --> 03:10.170
Do not fret.

03:10.711 --> 03:12.133
It only causes harm.

03:12.594 --> 03:19.725
For evil doers shall be cut off, but those who wait on the Lord, they shall inherit the earth."

03:21.228 --> 03:27.698
I'm about to share the title of this message in this series, but felt confirmation

03:28.034 --> 03:30.637
to kind of go this direction with this verse.

03:31.117 --> 03:33.459
So we talk about delight yourself in the Lord.

03:33.479 --> 03:37.503
He'll give you the desires of your heart pastor Rob last week, shared a quote from William Booth.

