05:56.252 --> 05:57.154
I'm rolling through everything.

05:57.214 --> 06:00.058
I was made for these healies with the greatest time of my life.

06:02.461 --> 06:03.202
Pack them back up.

06:06.166 --> 06:08.830
Clean them off, you know.

06:08.850 --> 06:09.812
Open them on Christmas.

06:11.033 --> 06:11.855
Put them back on.

06:13.677 --> 06:15.159
The, the bearings rusted.

