11:41.479 --> 11:44.282
The biggest thing that you think you could do for the kingdom.

11:45.183 --> 11:46.884
God's got even more for you.

11:47.485 --> 11:49.567
And that's the bonfire of life.

11:49.667 --> 11:51.749
That is the fire of life.

11:52.890 --> 11:54.852
But it's not about the fire.

11:55.833 --> 12:00.137
