12:06.036 --> 12:07.297
We're going deep into a metaphor.

12:07.477 --> 12:08.138
Everybody okay with it?

12:08.158 --> 12:08.859
I just stepped in the fire.

12:08.879 --> 12:12.824
I'm sorry.

12:12.844 --> 12:15.668
Because I like broke somebody's brain in here like, well, don't do that.

12:15.708 --> 12:16.008
Careful.

12:19.092 --> 12:22.276
The way the way that, yeah, Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego.

12:26.161 --> 12:29.906
The focus is not just saying, God, I want to bonfire season.

12:30.498 --> 12:32.100
I'm ready for the bonfire.

12:32.300 --> 12:34.383
I'm ready to be used by you in great ways.

12:34.403 --> 12:35.644
I've got gifts.

12:35.684 --> 12:36.546
