12:36.566 --> 12:38.708
I'm ready to be unleashed for the kingdom of God.

12:39.109 --> 12:40.410
Give me the bonfire.

12:41.952 --> 12:43.014
But that's not the right way to live.

12:43.875 --> 12:48.661
Because if you're focused on trees, again, we're going deep.

12:48.681 --> 12:55.249
If you're focused on just cutting down whole trees, you're not going to get them every day.

12:56.731 --> 12:58.553
Life's not like that.

12:58.573 --> 12:59.314
Not every day.

12:59.682 --> 13:00.543
