14:16.632 --> 14:18.234
And you will neglect those days.

14:18.555 --> 14:20.016
And you're not gonna pick up twigs.

14:20.998 --> 14:23.000
But God says, pick up the twig, bring it back.

14:23.961 --> 14:24.562
Bring it back.

14:25.282 --> 14:26.146
Put it on the fire.

14:26.748 --> 14:28.134
You need to tend to the fire.

14:28.154 --> 14:29.962
It's not about the bonfire season.

14:30.304 --> 14:34.019
It's about keeping the coals in your life hot.

14:34.040 --> 14:34.642
Let's add.

14:34.754 --> 14:35.716
to the fire.

14:35.736 --> 14:39.101
Let's add, if God's giving me a twig, I gotta pick up the twig.

14:39.121 --> 14:40.163
I gotta be faithful.

14:40.183 --> 14:40.984
I gotta be faithful.

14:41.044 --> 14:46.513
This looks like, this looks like, in serving people, it's like getting a 3 a.m. call and being the friend that you need to be.

14:46.773 --> 14:48.636
This is like, being the parent that you need to be.

14:48.857 --> 14:50.159
Giving time and energy.

14:50.179 --> 14:52.022
Being the spouse that you need to be.

14:52.062 --> 14:52.843
Being the leader.

14:53.544 --> 14:57.070
Giving words of encouragement to the person that annoys you at work.

14:57.631 --> 14:59.694
Like, you need to be used by God.

14:59.934 --> 15:02.258
And not every day is tree cutting season.

15:02.370 --> 15:03.431
But it's picking up twigs.

15:03.711 --> 15:05.033
Everybody cool with the metaphor so far?

15:06.414 --> 15:06.734
All right.

15:07.275 --> 15:10.258
It's the dreams in your heart, the big things that God's created you.

15:10.938 --> 15:15.183
Twig days look like this spiritually, spending time in the Word of God.

15:16.384 --> 15:21.429
Not every day, is it like, oh my gosh, this is amazing.

15:22.410 --> 15:24.872
Whoa, I didn't know that was in the Bible.

15:25.393 --> 15:27.495
Whoa, wow.

15:28.696 --> 15:30.738
There are days like that, and it's revelation.

15:31.362 --> 15:32.643
And it is life changing.

15:33.184 --> 15:37.789
But the Bible also says about itself that the Bible is alive and active.

15:37.809 --> 15:40.712
