15:52.285 --> 15:53.586
New revelation.

15:54.427 --> 15:54.907
Other days.

15:55.628 --> 15:57.270
I'm putting in time with God.

15:57.811 --> 16:01.074
I'm putting in time with God and you will learn.

16:01.346 --> 16:12.857
To love it, you will learn to crave it, not just craving the massive revelation, but craving this time with the Lord, spending time in the Word of God.

16:14.518 --> 16:18.842
Next one, spiritual twigs is spending time in prayer, in prayer.

16:19.183 --> 16:26.209
