I'm thankful for the gift of speaking in tongues because for me, my mind starts, I get distracted and it's like I have a tough time, you guys can tell.

16:46.231 --> 16:47.053
And so you know what?

16:47.073 --> 16:53.102
I can pray the perfect will of God by speaking in a prayer language, the gift of tongues.

16:54.384 --> 16:58.610
Spiritual twigs is serving in local church, serving, serving.

