17:17.503 --> 17:19.505
There's a way to learn, to love it.

17:19.885 --> 17:24.210
Nobody should hold a microphone if they're above setting up rows of chairs.

17:25.794 --> 17:27.258
Like that's amazing.

17:27.298 --> 17:30.187
God use me in the twig days in the twig days.

17:30.267 --> 17:35.282
I remember we had River Valley conference a few weeks back and we had

17:35.810 --> 17:57.579
churches from all around the country, come, River Valley Conference, we're pouring in, hey, this is what we do, we want to learn from you, this is awesome, we had spiritual moments, and I was asked to pray for needs of pastors, which is when you have 700 people in the room in today's day and age, that's like a huge group of people worshiping God, it's amazing, and I get to pray for needs, this is awesome.

17:58.580 --> 18:00.082
But if that was the thing,

18:00.226 --> 18:01.368
That's the fire.

18:01.428 --> 18:08.603
That's the thing that, yes, I was created to do that, but I neglect the twig days and neglect my family.

18:09.104 --> 18:12.451
Then all of this doesn't matter.

18:14.516 --> 18:15.417
All of it doesn't matter.

18:16.720 --> 18:17.682
I need to do.

18:17.762 --> 18:22.128
the twigs, because you never want to cut down a tree and drag it over cold coals.

18:22.408 --> 18:23.950
That's called the oversized gift.

18:24.231 --> 18:27.635
You've got a great gift, but you don't have the character to back it up.

18:27.976 --> 18:33.103
And so you get platformed, and then you get knocked off that platform because there's no character development.

18:33.443 --> 18:35.386
Everybody wants to talk about influence.

18:35.406 --> 18:37.429
Nobody wants to talk about character development.

18:37.769 --> 18:38.771
And that's a twig day.

18:39.311 --> 18:47.122
After twig day, you're tending to the heat of the coals, making sure they're hot so that the day God says, go cut down the tree,

18:47.330 --> 18:48.832
our hot coals ready to burn it.

18:50.194 --> 18:54.920
And so I'm praying over needs and feel like, man, I feel like I was created to do that.

18:54.940 --> 18:55.481
That's awesome.

18:55.541 --> 19:00.869
But my wife was having one of the worst days of her life with all four of our children.

19:02.871 --> 19:14.387
And I go home and learning this lesson, I would give all of this up to just make sure that I'm doing my job as a husband, as a father.

19:14.427 --> 19:16.530
Hey, you've got it.

19:17.410 --> 19:17.991
I'm with you.

19:18.251 --> 19:18.992
I'm fighting with you.

19:19.052 --> 19:20.014
I'm praying for you.

19:20.414 --> 19:21.937
I'm rebuking every devil.

19:23.218 --> 19:24.280
I'm doing my job.

19:25.021 --> 19:27.545
And I love that more than this.

19:27.585 --> 19:35.596
And you learn to just love every single day, not just bonfire days.

19:37.780 --> 19:42.526
This Psalm is talking about multiple ways of approaching life.

19:42.687 --> 19:45.010
One approach is to envy everybody else.

19:45.762 --> 19:47.264
and the things that they're getting to do.

19:47.944 --> 19:49.025
Well, why do they get to do it?

19:49.406 --> 19:50.267
I've got gifts too.

19:50.747 --> 19:51.748
I'm ready to be used too.

19:51.829 --> 19:54.011
Why are they advancing?

19:54.391 --> 19:55.653
Why do they get the promotion?

19:55.713 --> 19:57.194
Why do they get the pay raise?

19:57.575 --> 20:00.478
Why do they get the inflatable water park in the backyard?

20:00.498 --> 20:02.280
Why do they get to do that?

20:03.541 --> 20:15.634
One way to approach life, but the other is delighting in the Lord and watch Him give you the desires of your heart, trusting in the Lord.

20:16.386 --> 20:17.127
and doing good.

20:17.187 --> 20:19.669
It says, don't fret because of the Hebrew doers.

20:20.090 --> 20:21.671
Don't worry about everybody else.

20:23.353 --> 20:25.675
Trust in the Lord, delight in the Lord.

20:25.695 --> 20:31.380
1 John 2 15 says, do not love the world or the things in the world.

20:32.001 --> 20:35.044
If anybody loves the world, the love of the Father is not in Him.

20:35.905 --> 20:41.950
For all that is in the world, the desires of the flesh, the desires of the eyes and pride of life.

20:42.571 --> 20:45.874
It is not from the Father, but it is from the world.

20:46.434 --> 20:54.582
and the world is passing away, along with its desires, but whoever does, the will of God abides forever.

20:55.623 --> 21:02.089
It's learning to love the will of God more than the things of this world.

21:03.531 --> 21:05.252
We live in a culture of comparison.

21:05.272 --> 21:07.054
I'm just comparing my life to everybody else.

21:07.535 --> 21:08.496
Let's get rid of that.

21:08.976 --> 21:10.197
It will ruin your life.

21:11.478 --> 21:12.539
What's God called you to do?

21:13.741 --> 21:15.122
What's His will for your life?

21:16.162 --> 21:21.891
and watch Him move forward your life like a grappling hook.

21:21.911 --> 21:25.576
Don't delight yourself in your desires, but in the Lord.

21:27.158 --> 21:32.286
We're gonna close here in a second, and I'd love to end in worship so the band could come as well.

21:34.690 --> 21:43.182
Think about the Bible, these Bible heroes, heroes that did massive things for the kingdom of God.

21:43.202 --> 21:45.586
They're in the Bible, I mean, they're like, made it.

21:46.370 --> 21:47.431
They made it in the book.

21:48.272 --> 21:50.055
It's going to be an eternal book.

21:50.075 --> 21:51.276
These guys made it.

21:51.957 --> 21:53.579
It's awesome.

21:53.599 --> 21:55.321
They did fiery things.

21:58.205 --> 22:01.289
Joseph.

22:01.309 --> 22:09.799
Joseph, he had these dreams that he would one day rule over his brothers and his father.

22:10.820 --> 22:12.082
He told those dreams.

22:13.602 --> 22:16.565
got him into a scenario where he was sold in his slavery.

22:17.887 --> 22:19.989
When did he have those dreams?

22:21.571 --> 22:25.215
And then when did those dreams come to fruition?

22:27.457 --> 22:35.406
I think he was about 17 years old, 17 years old having the dreams like I was made for big things.

22:36.267 --> 22:42.994
And you've got dreams in your heart, things that God made you for, wired you for to do big things for the kingdom of God.

22:43.202 --> 22:45.846
Hopefully you do because it's the truth.

22:45.866 --> 22:48.249
God made you to do things for his kingdom.

22:48.269 --> 22:49.010
And it's amazing.

22:49.130 --> 22:51.394
It's beyond what you could ask, think, or imagine.

22:51.414 --> 22:53.837
He's got great plans for your life.

22:54.979 --> 23:01.328
Joseph, having those dreams at 17, when did that dream come to fruition?

23:02.349 --> 23:11.282
When he was 17 and a half, waited six months, little six months, there's some people that are like, I've been in this internship for six months.

23:12.706 --> 23:13.627
I'm ready to preach.

23:14.508 --> 23:15.369
I'm ready to plant.

23:15.449 --> 23:16.109
I'm ready to go.

23:16.149 --> 23:21.054
You've been working a job.

23:22.496 --> 23:25.739
Like, hey, I've been here for, I've been here for one year.

23:25.779 --> 23:27.620
I'm ready for the promotion.

23:27.681 --> 23:30.263
I'm ready for the, I got more in there.

23:30.283 --> 23:32.826
I wish somebody would recognize what's in me.

23:33.967 --> 23:37.690
You can identify with this feeling of like this delay.

23:38.791 --> 23:41.554
Joseph wasn't until he was 30.

23:42.082 --> 23:44.165
We're talking 13 years.

23:45.326 --> 23:50.392
And maybe there's people in this room that you've been serving Jesus for a long time and you've waited 13 years for something.

23:50.412 --> 23:56.580
But isn't it awesome that that thing comes to pass and you know that the Lord made it happen and you didn't force it?

23:57.802 --> 23:58.843
Man, that feels good.

23:59.003 --> 24:00.025
God, you did this.

24:00.165 --> 24:01.707
I didn't force this.

24:02.207 --> 24:05.031
I'm picking up twigs day after day after day after day after day.

24:05.091 --> 24:06.272
I'm tending to the coals.

24:06.693 --> 24:10.738
And then 13 years later for Joseph, it's his tree cutting day.

24:11.618 --> 24:13.341
Bonfire season, this is amazing.

24:13.441 --> 24:14.363
Think about David.

24:15.204 --> 24:20.032
King David, anointed to be the next king of Israel, the second king.

24:20.753 --> 24:22.376
How old was he when he was anointed?

24:22.957 --> 24:25.962
One, his dad forgot about him out in the past year.

24:26.583 --> 24:29.007
Like Samuel was like, you got any more sons?

24:29.868 --> 24:30.529
He's like, oh.

24:33.074 --> 24:33.655
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

24:34.796 --> 24:35.397
I got one more.

24:35.417 --> 24:36.279
Yeah, yeah, yeah, David.

24:36.299 --> 24:38.162
David, get in here.

24:40.066 --> 24:42.009
And David comes in, same as like you.

24:43.271 --> 24:48.639
God said it, you are the next king of Israel.

24:48.659 --> 24:51.103
And he's like, dump the oil all over me.

24:51.203 --> 24:52.305
This is awesome.

24:52.325 --> 24:53.366
I'm the next king.

24:53.406 --> 24:54.208
Eat it.

24:54.228 --> 24:55.670
He's like talking to his brothers.

24:58.474 --> 24:59.255
That's not in the Bible.

25:01.959 --> 25:02.621
Poor the oil.

25:02.721 --> 25:03.181
Poor the oil.

25:03.201 --> 25:04.804
He's 15 years old.

25:06.767 --> 25:08.850
When did he become the king?

25:11.010 --> 25:12.252
wasn't until he was 30.

25:13.754 --> 25:15.296
So Joseph waited 13 years.

25:16.117 --> 25:24.427
David waits 15 years for the bonfire, for the tree cutting season, where it comes to pass.

25:26.029 --> 25:33.099
Man, I've been waiting, I've been waiting four years, four years and I don't have my dream home yet.

25:33.119 --> 25:35.361
I don't have my dream job yet.

25:36.503 --> 25:38.866
Nobody's looking at me, nobody sees me.

25:39.138 --> 25:40.880
God saw David, he'll see you.

25:43.162 --> 25:44.043
Think about Jesus.

25:44.384 --> 25:46.967
This one is crazy.

25:46.987 --> 25:47.788
Think about Jesus.

25:48.608 --> 25:49.289
Son of God.

25:50.831 --> 25:51.672
Born of a virgin.

25:53.073 --> 25:56.097
But he wasn't like fully God, fully man.

25:56.137 --> 26:00.241
He wasn't born all knowing like as a baby.

26:00.341 --> 26:05.647
Like he wasn't like a two year old toddler like, Cheryl, I know what you did.

26:07.449 --> 26:08.050
Bobby.

26:08.674 --> 26:09.315
You're doing great.

26:09.395 --> 26:09.816
Keep it up.

26:10.216 --> 26:14.061
You know, the Bible says he grew in wisdom and stature.

26:14.562 --> 26:29.262
He grew, but at some point he realized he knew that at some point he knew that he was the son of God, the Messiah, the anointed one, the one who came to save all of humanity, to make a way where there was no way.

26:29.382 --> 26:30.023
When did he know?

26:31.585 --> 26:35.090
We're not exactly sure, but there's a story when he was 12 years old.

26:36.130 --> 26:41.455
And his parents forgot him for three days in Jerusalem, which is, I don't know how that happens.

26:41.535 --> 26:45.619
I mean, that's, that is like, you're gonna lose your kids if that happens today.

26:45.959 --> 26:48.082
You can't forget your kids for three days.

26:49.643 --> 26:50.604
And they're like, where's Jesus?

26:50.644 --> 26:51.205
Where's Jesus?

26:51.245 --> 26:51.725
Where's Jesus?

26:51.785 --> 26:52.206
We lost.

26:52.266 --> 26:53.086
We don't know where he is.

26:53.747 --> 26:55.168
And they make it back to the temple.

26:56.289 --> 27:00.874
And Jesus is teaching at 12 years old.

27:02.856 --> 27:05.138
And they're like, what were you doing?

27:06.146 --> 27:06.927
What were you doing?

27:07.247 --> 27:09.210
In my mind, Jesus goes, what were you doing?

27:09.710 --> 27:10.151
Mom?

27:13.956 --> 27:14.597
He didn't say that.

27:16.058 --> 27:19.102
He said, don't you know at 12 years old?

27:20.163 --> 27:22.466
Don't you know that I need to be about my father's business?

27:23.247 --> 27:24.809
Not talking about his earthly father.

27:25.710 --> 27:27.052
Talking about his heavenly father.

27:27.733 --> 27:29.916
He knows he's the Messiah.

27:29.936 --> 27:30.697
12 years old.

27:32.639 --> 27:35.122
When did he perform his first miracle?

27:36.770 --> 27:38.052
when he was 30 years old.

27:39.975 --> 27:41.357
Think about the Son of God.

27:41.377 --> 27:44.622
You've got big dreams for your life.

27:45.744 --> 27:46.745
You're not the Son of God.

27:49.209 --> 27:52.233
You're gonna do great things with the power of the Holy Spirit.

27:52.714 --> 27:55.118
Jesus said you'll do even greater things than he did.

27:55.899 --> 27:57.361
Big things, big things, you will.

27:58.383 --> 28:04.131
But Jesus is 12 years old and waits 18 years to perform his first miracle.

28:04.211 --> 28:06.034
How many blind people did he walk by?

28:06.402 --> 28:09.305
at 13 years old, at 14 years old.

28:09.705 --> 28:16.972
How many people that couldn't walk, he saw him knowing that he was the answer, knowing that he had the power and the authority.

28:17.653 --> 28:19.394
It was him, he's the solution.

28:19.515 --> 28:21.436
How many people, how many needs did he see?

28:22.377 --> 28:33.168
Yet he waited for the will of the Father, your will, not mine, your timing, not mine.

28:33.988 --> 28:35.730
He waited 18 years.

28:36.962 --> 28:42.307
And in God's perfect timing, He completed everything He was called to do.

28:43.949 --> 28:45.330
What are the dreams in your heart?

28:47.672 --> 28:48.994
What has God created you to do?

28:49.094 --> 28:51.336
That's the fire.

28:52.897 --> 28:55.520
But it's not about the fire.

28:56.381 --> 28:57.702
It's about the will of the Father.

28:57.802 --> 28:59.023
Today is a twig day.

29:00.625 --> 29:01.766
I'm going to learn to love this.

29:02.547 --> 29:03.227
I'm going to pick it up.

29:03.487 --> 29:04.448
I'm going to throw it on the fire.

29:04.769 --> 29:06.130
Tomorrow, another twig day.

29:07.490 --> 29:09.914
By the way, Jesus during his ministry had twig days.

29:09.934 --> 29:10.314
Think about it.

29:10.755 --> 29:11.877
He had to walk everywhere.

29:14.280 --> 29:15.963
Not every day was like revival day.

29:16.003 --> 29:20.049
It was like, oh, we got to walk five days, you know?

29:21.351 --> 29:21.931
In twig days.

29:24.035 --> 29:34.450
But if you keep the coals hot in your life, if you keep them hot in your life, God's going to give you a chainsaw in this tree cut in season.

29:35.874 --> 29:39.640
You wanna make sure that those coals are hot to have the bonfire.

29:39.660 --> 29:44.367
But even then, in the middle of a bonfire, it's not about the fire.

29:44.387 --> 29:45.388
It's about the next day.

29:45.408 --> 29:48.133
I got more twigs and I love it.

29:49.094 --> 29:53.320
I love this life following Jesus.

29:53.441 --> 29:57.186
It's the greatest adventure of all time, the most thrilling thing.

29:57.547 --> 30:02.935
There is a way to feed on his faithfulness and to love and enjoy faithfulness.

30:03.776 --> 30:04.978
I'm gonna sing in just a second.

30:06.050 --> 30:06.891
Like we stand to our feet.

30:07.992 --> 30:08.773
Lord, we thank You.

30:10.555 --> 30:14.459
We thank You that You have created people in this room right now.

30:15.160 --> 30:19.866
People watching online, You've created them for great things for Your Kingdom.

30:21.067 --> 30:24.351
And Lord, we pray that those things would come to pass, but they would come to pass.

30:25.272 --> 30:34.482
Living our lives faithful to the will of the Father, that we would do everything You've asked us to do along the way, keeping the coals hot in our life.

30:35.042 --> 30:36.784
Because fires tend to go out.

30:38.026 --> 30:42.512
Help us keep the colds hot so that we can accomplish in your timing.

30:42.732 --> 30:44.174
All you've created is to accomplish.

30:44.194 --> 30:46.037
Help us live meek.

30:46.678 --> 30:48.020
It's a description of Jesus.

30:48.661 --> 30:57.152
Calm, content, quietly patient, living biblical lives, moral lives.

30:59.255 --> 30:59.656
Help us.

31:02.640 --> 31:04.402
And Lord, I pray for anybody here

31:06.786 --> 31:14.037
Anybody that can hear my voice right now that's been pursuing their desires instead of delighting in the Lord.

31:14.938 --> 31:20.306
I pray that there would be repentance in our heart and a turning to you.

31:21.087 --> 31:22.949
Lord, it's your presence that we want.

31:23.070 --> 31:26.615
It's your will that we want more than the desires of our heart.

31:27.877 --> 31:34.386
And as we delight in you, Lord, we know that it's going to come to pass.

31:34.946 --> 31:37.742
the desires of our heart in line with your will.

31:38.848 --> 31:41.262
We thank you for it in Jesus' name, everybody said.

31:42.066 --> 31:42.569
Amen.

